title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Apr 8 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Apr 8 2022
description:
The only way to stop the crime wave that's getting worse all over the country is to lock up criminals. C&B take a call from a true Southerner. Alaska GOP Senate candidate Kelly Tshibaka joins Clay and Buck to discuss how she plans to beat Lisa Murkowski. Walmart to pay truckers up to $110,000. Clay extols the virtue of Zaxby's chicken tender sauce.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
